nodes.text: Archduke was a title of nobility. It was the title of the ruler of Geonosis, or Stalgasin hive, the planet's ruling hive. A symbol of their position was the Archduke's Staff of Command. Notable Archdukes included Hadiss the Vaulted and Poggle the Lesser.
Monio of the Dentamma Nebula was an Archduke.
